description:
Enrich hotel records in the OrientDB `demodb` database (URL: http://localhost:2480/studio/index.html, Server: `root` / `GymAnything123!`, DB: `admin` / `admin`). Add an `Amenities` property (EMBEDDEDLIST of Strings) and a `SocialMedia` property (EMBEDDEDMAP) to the `Hotels` class. Update the following hotels with their respective data:

- Hotel Artemide: Amenities ["WiFi", "Restaurant", "Concierge", "Air Conditioning"], SocialMedia {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/HotelArtemide", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/hotelartemide"}
- Hotel Adlon Kempinski: Amenities ["WiFi", "Pool", "Spa", "Restaurant", "Gym", "Concierge"], SocialMedia {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/HotelAdlon", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/HotelAdlon", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/hoteladlon"}
- The Savoy: Amenities ["WiFi", "Pool", "Restaurant", "Bar", "Concierge", "Room Service"], SocialMedia {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/TheSavoyLondon", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/thesavoylondon"}
- Park Hyatt Tokyo: Amenities ["WiFi", "Pool", "Spa", "Gym", "Restaurant", "Bar", "Concierge"], SocialMedia {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/ParkHyattTokyo", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/parkhyatttokyo", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/ParkHyattTokyo"}
- Copacabana Palace: Amenities ["WiFi", "Pool", "Spa", "Restaurant", "Bar", "Beach Access"], SocialMedia {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/CopaPalace", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/copacabanapalace"}

Identify all hotels containing "Pool" in their `Amenities` list and export their names as a JSON list of strings to /home/ga/Documents/hotels_with_pool.json.
